{"tid":2453181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美資大行女高層涉嫌逃避強制檢疫失蹤　丈夫早前確診","createTime":"2021-03-19T09:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T11:34:16.000Z","uid":68360,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"95ff0a32f25680188ddf521ac0c7e59366cb5676","tid":2453181,"uid":68360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情反覆，西營盤健身室URSUS Fitness爆疫群組更蔓延至金融界。《香港01》接獲消息指，一間美資投資管理公司的女高層，被列為密切接觸者須強制檢疫隔離，但卻失蹤，當局或會通緝。消息指，她早前確診的丈夫，亦是另一間美資投行的員工。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑入住高級酒店 當局或通緝</strong><br />\n該名失蹤的女高層，現年40多歲，在一間美資的投資管理公司香港分公司工作約六七年。《香港01》接獲消息指，她被列為密切接觸者後失蹤，懷疑私下入住一間高級酒店，逃避強制檢疫，當局或通緝。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210319/449606970278678528324705.jpeg/f6_uccAWA6WaP8mrHmod3Y0bZH0KDSpR4ufB0-LnwdM?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210319%2F449606970278678528324705.jpeg%2Ff6_uccAWA6WaP8mrHmod3Y0bZH0KDSpR4ufB0-LnwdM%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=d70a198b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"168b8f0526d9c55c86778d334fc0a97fbbc6234e","tid":2453181,"uid":68360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"有無人知邊間大行咁叻叻豬"},{"pid":"5db17c59a68a74687bdb3a805b984ecc2b5cf37b","tid":2453181,"uid":59567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"人民日報：美國間諜公然潛逃播毒"},{"pid":"f855a26ee794d05b9fae0b42cca18da85587f9c7","tid":2453181,"uid":364041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"做咩要遮住個樣？"},{"pid":"e6e27ef27d188320302b3bd983cdfda9650f8b94","tid":2453181,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"危害國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b8dea170c41b169a342463be123e36c142683","tid":2453181,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f855a26ee794d05b9fae0b42cca18da85587f9c7","tid":2453181,"uid":364041,"like":1